headline: Here’s Some Advice for Airbnb Hosts: Smile in Your Profile Picture
summary: When it comes to  Airbnb  bookings, a smile can go a long way.  In one experiment, the researchers asked participants several questions, including: “How certain are you that the interactions with the host will be positive?” Those who saw a smiling host rated their expected interactions with the host 6.03 on a 9-point scale (with 9 being “very certain” and 1 being “not at all certain”) compared with 4.86 when the host didn’t smile.
